    <p>This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module <b>test3</b> <br>(Source path: <i>META-INF/yang/test3.yang</i>): <pre> list device { key "d-id" leaf d-id { type string; } leaf d-type { type d-type-type; } leaf ip-address { type string; } leaf d-name { type string; } leaf img-id { type string; } uses device-grouping; } </pre> The schema path to identify an instance is <i>test3/devices/device</i> <p>To create instances of this class use DeviceBuilder.
